First time installing the project, activate the virtual environment and add the symlinks:

$ mv $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/postactivate $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/postactivate_org
$ ln -s `pwd`/_virtualenv/postactivate_xxx $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/postactivate
(where xxx is local/prod/test)

$ mv $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/predeactivate $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/predeactivate_org
$ ln -s `pwd`/_virtualenv/predeactivate $VIRTUAL_ENV/bin/predeactivate
